    "record_zh": "烏犧奧泥在沃瓦倫與台北市議員相遇，參與調查山米克死亡與沃瓦倫詛咒，拜訪鎮長家、寂靜殿與魏斯科。穿越嚎叫森林時，他與同伴吃下有毒三明治，遭遇狼群襲擊，並經歷部分成員死亡後又復甦的異常事件。\n\n眾人帶回葛蘭倫大法師後，沃瓦倫的驅咒儀式變成屠殺。烏犧奧泥與倖存者進入寂靜殿地下城，並與家亨、烏柯一同聽見多姆尼爾的聲音，被要求在冒險團中完成玩笑。烏犧奧泥在地下城中將被俘虜的哥布林加冕為「地底王神王尼可」。\n\n寇林菲爾德後，隊伍前往麥克嵩途中，烏犧奧泥悄悄帶著神王尼可跳下馬車，與其他夥伴暫時告別。",
    "record_en": "Usioni met the Taipei City Councilors in Vowalon and joined the investigation into Shanmik's death and the curse on Vowalon, visiting the mayor's house, the Temple of Silence, and Weisco. While crossing the Howling Forest, he and his companions ate poisoned sandwiches, were attacked by wolves, and experienced the abnormal event in which several members died and then revived.\n\nAfter the group brought back Archmage Granlen, Vowalon's curse-breaking ritual turned into a massacre. Usioni and the survivors entered the dungeon beneath the Temple of Silence, where he, Jiaheng, and Uko heard Domneil's voice and were told to complete jokes within the adventuring party. In the dungeon, Usioni crowned a captured goblin as the underground king, God-King Knicol.\n\nAfter Korringfield, while the party was traveling toward Macksohn, Usioni quietly jumped off the carriage with God-King Knicol and temporarily parted ways with the others."
  },
