    "record_zh": "米多莉在沃瓦倫加入台北市議員，接受潔絲敏委託，前往魏斯科尋找葛蘭倫大法師。旅途中，他因潔絲敏準備的三明治中毒，也曾在過橋時被河水沖走，幾乎溺死，並在津菈的庇護下爬上岸。此事之後，他與部分同伴發生摩擦。\n\n沃瓦倫儀式失控時，米多莉因獨自行動而被同伴質疑，之後道歉並繼續進入寂靜殿地下城。後來他經歷寇林菲爾德、麥克嵩、麥丁頓餘波與妖精荒野事件。在多倫維爾，雷米消失的爆炸中，米多莉失去左前臂；之後他得到金屬手臂，並持續參與巫妖之手與滿月前的事件。",
    "record_en": "Midori joined the Taipei City Councilors in Vowalon, accepted Jasmine's commission, and went to Weisco to find Archmage Granlen. During the journey, he was poisoned by sandwiches prepared by Jasmine, and he was also swept away by the river while crossing a bridge, nearly drowning before climbing ashore under Tsuna's protection. After this incident, friction arose between him and some of his companions.\n\nWhen the Vowalon ritual went out of control, Midori was questioned by his companions for acting alone. He later apologized and continued into the dungeon beneath the Temple of Silence. He subsequently went through Korringfield, Macksohn, the aftermath of Mattington, and the Feywild incident. In Dolenville, during the explosion in which Lemmy disappeared, Midori lost his left forearm; afterward, he received a metal arm and continued to take part in the Hand of the Lich and the events before the full moon."
  },
