    "record_zh": "帕拉丁在沃瓦倫與台北市議員同行，參與調查詛咒、前往魏斯科、穿越嚎叫森林，並帶回葛蘭倫大法師。他經歷毒三明治、狼群戰鬥、死亡與復甦，以及沃瓦倫儀式中鎮民化為屍體與殭屍的事件，之後進入寂靜殿地下城。\n\n在寇林菲爾德，帕拉丁為拯救病危的父親，割下了自己的耳朵來做月神芬諾爾的交易儀式。他也得知自己的生母是麥克嵩的紫羅蘭珊吉雅。前往麥克嵩後，他與生母相認，並被封為新任寇林菲爾德爵士。\n\n家亨與安納戴克死後，隊伍在朗甫頓分家：米多莉等人帶波前往方努爾，帕拉丁爵士則與蘇加魯、墜兒前往瑟巴諾追查拉索斯教。之後他又參與瑟巴諾與阿爾芬諾相關事件。最終，帕拉丁遭被奪舍的蜘蛛神教神明「母親大人」鑽入其體內而死去。麥丁頓王國為其舉行了國葬。",
    "record_en": "Paladin traveled with the Taipei City Councilors in Vowalon, taking part in the curse investigation, the trip to Weisco, the crossing of the Howling Forest, and the return of Archmage Granlen. He experienced the poisoned sandwiches, the wolf battle, death and revival, and the incident in which Vowalon's ritual turned the townspeople into corpses and zombies, after which he entered the dungeon beneath the Temple of Silence.\n\nIn Korringfield, Paladin cut off his own ear to perform a ritual bargain with the moon god Fenor in order to save his dying father. He also learned that his birth mother was Sangia Violet of Macksohn. After reaching Macksohn, he reunited with his birth mother and was named the new Syr Korringfield.\n\nAfter Jiaheng and Anedak died, the party split in Lompton: Midori and the others took Bo to Fanor, while Syr Paladin went with Sugalu and Drayer to Sebano to investigate the Rathos cult. He later took part in events related to Sebano and Alfenor. In the end, Paladin died when the possessed deity of the Spider God cult, Mother, entered his body. The Kingdom of Mattington held a state funeral for him."
  },
