    "record_zh": "烏柯在沃瓦倫加入台北市議員，以德魯伊的經驗帶領隊伍穿越嚎叫森林，並在路邊讀出德魯伊語留下的訊息。狼群襲擊中，他與同伴經歷瀕死與復甦。沃瓦倫儀式失控時，他化身動物，背起倒地的薩梅爾與 YHWH，與其他倖存者衝入寂靜殿。\n\n進入地下城後，烏柯與家亨、烏犧奧泥一同聽見多姆尼爾的呼喚。他協助被囚的崔夏，並在背著她前進時，讓神秘石頭融入崔夏體內。後來崔夏因拉索斯教威脅父母而決定回去面對危機，烏柯選擇跟隨她離開隊伍。",
    "record_en": "Uko joined the Taipei City Councilors in Vowalon. Drawing on his experience as a druid, he led the party through the Howling Forest and read messages left in Druidic by the roadside. During the wolf attack, he and his companions experienced near death and revival. When the Vowalon ritual went out of control, he transformed into an animal, carried the fallen Samael and YHWH on his back, and rushed into the Temple of Silence with the other survivors.\n\nAfter entering the dungeon, Uko heard Domneil's call together with Jiaheng and Usioni. He helped the imprisoned Trisha, and while carrying her onward, allowed a mysterious stone to merge into Trisha's body. Later, when Trisha decided to return and face the danger because the Rathos cult was threatening her parents, Uko chose to follow her and leave the party."
  },
