    "record_zh": "龍恩在沃瓦倫加入台北市議員，參與鎮長委託、嚎叫森林行軍、狼群戰鬥與沃瓦倫驅咒儀式。儀式失控時，他踏出黑暗與寂靜，發現周圍滿是鎮民屍體與殭屍，並與後來化身為冰原狼的烏柯衝向葛蘭倫。\n\n之後龍恩經歷寂靜殿地下城、洛林精神、寇林菲爾德、麥克嵩與 Plus 的後續事件。巫妖之手篇中，他在大學城禁書區接觸與「手與眼睛」相關的書並一度消失。回歸後，他與茜卓博士衝突；在同伴試圖帶走他時，迷霧散去後只剩垂落的繩子，龍恩與茜卓博士皮衣一同不見。",
    "record_en": "Ron joined the Taipei City Councilors in Vowalon and took part in the mayor's commission, the march through the Howling Forest, the wolf battle, and Vowalon's curse-breaking ritual. When the ritual went out of control, he stepped out of the darkness and silence, found the area filled with townspeople's corpses and zombies, and charged toward Granlen together with Uko, who had transformed into a winter wolf.\n\nRon later went through the dungeon beneath the Temple of Silence, the spirit of Lorin, Korringfield, Macksohn, and the later Plus events. In the Hand of the Lich, he encountered a book connected to the Hand and Eye in the restricted section of University City and disappeared for a time. After returning, he came into conflict with Dr. Xandria; when his companions tried to take him away, the mist cleared and only a dangling rope remained. Ron and Dr. Xandria's leather coat had vanished together."
  },
