    "record_zh": "薩梅爾在沃瓦倫加入台北市議員，參與詛咒調查、魏斯科之行與嚎叫森林行軍。他在森林中與家亨輪流守夜，也在重返森林途中撿到一隻親近自己的幼狼，並為牠取名酷爆。沃瓦倫儀式失控後，他在虛弱中看見黑影推開寂靜殿大門，提醒眾人追入地下。\n\n地下城中，薩梅爾與被囚禁的崔夏談話，因她被背叛與囚禁的經歷想起自己的過往。之後他前往寇林菲爾德、麥克嵩與麥丁頓，並參與妖精荒野、巫妖之手與滿月前的事件。薩梅爾在妖精荒野遇見了自己「已死」的祖母英荻格，也學會了自由穿越妖精荒野與物質世界的魔法。",
    "record_en": "Samael joined the Taipei City Councilors in Vowalon and took part in the curse investigation, the trip to Weisco, and the march through the Howling Forest. In the forest, he took turns keeping watch with Jiaheng, and on the return through the woods he found a wolf cub that had taken a liking to him, naming it Kubao. After the Vowalon ritual went out of control, he saw a black shadow push open the doors of the Temple of Silence while he was weakened, prompting the group to pursue it underground.\n\nIn the dungeon, Samael spoke with the imprisoned Trisha, whose betrayal and captivity reminded him of his own past. He later went to Korringfield, Macksohn, and Mattington, and took part in the Feywild, Hand of the Lich, and pre-full-moon events. In the Feywild, Samael met his supposedly dead grandmother Indig, and also learned magic that allowed him to move freely between the Feywild and the Material World."
  },
