    "record_zh": "家亨在沃瓦倫加入台北市議員，參與詛咒調查、魏斯科之行與嚎叫森林行軍。他曾因潔絲敏準備的三明治中毒，也在狼群戰鬥中經歷死亡與復甦。沃瓦倫毀滅後，他隨倖存者進入寂靜殿地下城，並與烏柯、烏犧奧泥一同聽見多姆尼爾的聲音。\n\n麥克嵩篇中，家亨曾被士兵帶走，後來於角鬥士事件中被釋放並與隊友重逢。比武大會慘劇後，他與安納戴克、雷米離去後未歸；雷米後來帶回消息，說家亨與安納戴克被殺。眾人沿城牆找到家亨被斬首的遺體，他的右手將安納戴克的頭按在地上。隊伍挖墓後將他安葬。",
    "record_en": "Jiaheng joined the Taipei City Councilors in Vowalon and took part in the curse investigation, the trip to Weisco, and the march through the Howling Forest. He was poisoned by sandwiches prepared by Jasmine, and during the wolf battle he experienced death and revival. After Vowalon's destruction, he entered the dungeon beneath the Temple of Silence with the survivors, and heard Domneil's voice together with Uko and Usioni.\n\nIn the Macksohn arc, Jiaheng was taken away by soldiers, then later released during the gladiator incident and reunited with his teammates. After the tragedy at the tournament, he left with Anedak and Lemmy and did not return; Lemmy later brought back word that Jiaheng and Anedak had been killed. The group found Jiaheng's decapitated body along the city wall, with his right hand pressing Anedak's head to the ground. The party dug a grave and buried him."
  },
