    "record_zh": "Tai Tai我還要在沃瓦倫加入台北市議員，參與鎮長委託、魏斯科之行與嚎叫森林行軍。他曾在巴姆的雜貨店買下神秘項鍊。米多莉因落水事件對他出手並搶奪背包時，他選擇不正面衝突，將背包與項鍊交給米多莉。\n\n回到沃瓦倫後，台北市議員受到鎮民款待，參加慶祝葛蘭倫歸來的派對。當晚，YHWH 以 Tai Tai我還要老師的身份出現。Tai Tai我還要決定皈依拉索斯教，與 YHWH 前往寂靜殿。隔日驅咒儀式開始前，寇頓神父表示 Tai Tai我還要一早已被派去執行任務，因此沒有出現在沃瓦倫毀滅的現場。",
    "record_en": "Tai Tai Wo Hai Yao joined the Taipei City Councilors in Vowalon and took part in the mayor's commission, the trip to Weisco, and the march through the Howling Forest. At Bam's general store, he purchased a mysterious necklace. When Midori attacked him and seized his backpack after the river incident, he chose not to confront him directly and handed both the backpack and necklace to Midori.\n\nAfter returning to Vowalon, the Taipei City Councilors were hosted by the townspeople and attended a party celebrating Granlen's return. That night, YHWH appeared as Tai Tai Wo Hai Yao's teacher. Tai Tai Wo Hai Yao decided to convert to the Rathos cult and went with YHWH to the Temple of Silence. Before the curse-breaking ritual began the next day, Father Cotton said that Tai Tai Wo Hai Yao had already been sent on a mission early that morning, so he was not present at the destruction of Vowalon."
  },
