    "record_zh": "YHWH在沃瓦倫慶功夜以 Tai Tai我還要老師的身份登場，隨後加入台北市議員。沃瓦倫儀式失控後，他與倖存者一同進入寂靜殿地下城。地下城中，他曾從異界傳送回來後，以法術射殺正在宣言的哥布林王，使剩餘哥布林逃散。\n\n之後 YHWH 前往寇林菲爾德、麥克嵩、麥丁頓與多倫維爾。在雷米爆炸消失後，他取走雷米留下的項鍊掛在自己脖子上。他參與妖精荒野失守、巫妖之手與滿月前事件。在大學城，龍恩與茜卓博士皮衣消失後，YHWH 要求同伴找到茜卓博士的皮衣，自己進入茜卓博士家並關上門。最終，YHWH 繼承茜卓博士在大學城的房子，並與冒險者前往方努爾市。",
    "record_en": "YHWH appeared on the night of Vowalon's celebration as Tai Tai Wo Hai Yao's teacher, then joined the Taipei City Councilors. After the Vowalon ritual went out of control, he entered the dungeon beneath the Temple of Silence with the survivors. In the dungeon, after being transported back from another plane, he used magic to shoot down the goblin king while the king was making a proclamation, causing the remaining goblins to scatter.\n\nYHWH later went to Korringfield, Macksohn, Mattington, and Dolenville. After Lemmy vanished in the explosion, he took the necklace Lemmy left behind and wore it around his own neck. He took part in the fall of the Feywild, the Hand of the Lich, and the events before the full moon. In University City, after Ron and Dr. Xandria's leather coat disappeared, YHWH asked his companions to find Dr. Xandria's coat, then entered Dr. Xandria's house and closed the door. In the end, YHWH inherited Dr. Xandria's house in University City and went with the adventurers to Fanor City."
  },
