    "record_zh": "雷米在寇林菲爾德加入台北市議員，與隊伍一同經歷寇林菲爾德街道、好地方與生死之間的事件。雷米接著脫隊，並未與冒險者們同時前往麥克嵩。也因此，一名易容者取代他的身份，靠近冒險者團隊。\n\n在麥克嵩比武大會，雷米終於回歸。然而，比武大會後後，雷米與家亨、安納戴克一同離去，卻只有他回來，並帶回兩人被殺的消息。他後來向米多莉談起家亨與安納戴克遇害的經過。在多倫維爾夜裡，米多莉祈禱時爆炸發生，雷米消失，只留下肉塊、衣物與項鍊。雷米在意識消失前聽見熟悉聲音呼喚自己離去。",
    "record_en": "Lemmy joined the Taipei City Councilors in Korringfield and went through the events of Korringfield's streets, the Good Place, and the space between life and death with the party. Lemmy then separated from the group and did not travel to Macksohn at the same time as the adventurers. As a result, a disguised impostor took his place and approached the adventuring party.\n\nAt the Macksohn tournament, Lemmy finally returned. However, after the tournament, Lemmy left together with Jiaheng and Anedak, but only he came back, bringing news that the other two had been killed. He later told Midori what had happened to Jiaheng and Anedak. During the night in Dolenville, an explosion occurred while Midori was praying, and Lemmy disappeared, leaving only flesh, clothing, and a necklace behind. Before losing consciousness, Lemmy heard a familiar voice calling him away."
