    "record_zh": "喜利・歐喜利在麥克嵩比武大會事件中登場，之後加入台北市議員後續行動。他參與麥丁頓餘波，並在與米多莉、龍恩、薩梅爾、YHWH 等人同行，前往多倫維爾、妖精荒野、大學城與方努爾相關地點。\n\n在多倫維爾，白醫師以白光帶走多名同伴時，喜利・歐喜利靠意志抵抗，醒來後發現房內只剩自己與法朗茲。巫妖之手篇中，他曾獨自離開隊伍一段時間，表示需要靜一靜，晚上再於茜卓博士家會合。之後他協助調查龍恩失蹤、茜卓博士皮衣與艾麗克斯工作舖相關事件。",
    "record_en": "Siri Oslee appeared during the Macksohn tournament incident and later joined the Taipei City Councilors' subsequent actions. He took part in the aftermath of Mattington, traveling with Midori, Ron, Samael, YHWH, and others to Dolenville, the Feywild, University City, and locations connected to Fanor.\n\nIn Dolenville, when Dr. White used white light to take away several companions, Siri Oslee resisted through willpower. After waking, he found that only he and Franz remained in the room. During the Hand of the Lich, he left the party alone for a time, saying he needed quiet and would regroup at Dr. Xandria's house that evening. Afterward, he helped investigate Ron's disappearance, Dr. Xandria's leather coat, and events connected to Alex's workshop."
  },
  {
    "name_en": "Tweeter",
    "name_zh": "圖伊特",
    "race_en": "Aarakocra",
    "race_zh": "天狗",
    "class_en": [
