    "record_zh": "圖伊特在麥丁頓破碎篇登場，與帕拉丁、蘇加魯、華生等人走入惡棍之城，接著參與交易、真實形態與阿爾芬諾之禮。阿爾芬諾事件中，他調查蜘蛛王相關書籍，也在王宮與奧利佛同行。\n\n之後圖伊特前往潛伏的危機與洛森王國。月光狩獵會襲擊時，他失去意識並在黑暗中聽見宗主的聲音，醒來後得知攻擊者是月神支派。後續他參與劇院之下、母親重生、複製體、月光狩獵會、孵化而出的夥伴與深入洛森等事件。最終，圖伊特在異變的母親大人屠殺中，與芬諾爾做交易，以自己存在的現實與記憶，換取羅特的安危。",
    "record_en": "Tweeter appeared in the Shattered Mattington arc, entering the City of Villains with Paladin, Sugalu, Watson, and others, then taking part in the Deal, True Form, and Gift of Alfenor. During the Alfenor incident, he investigated books related to the Spider King and also traveled with Oliver in the palace.\n\nTweeter later went into the Hidden Crisis and the Kingdom of Losen. During the Moonlight Hunt attack, he lost consciousness and heard the patron's voice in the darkness; after waking, he learned that the attackers belonged to a branch of the moon god. He later took part in Under the Theater, Mother's Rebirth, the clones, the Moonlight Hunt, the Hatched Companion, and Into Losen. In the end, during the transformed Mother's massacre, Tweeter made a bargain with Fenor, exchanging the reality and memory of his own existence for Lott's safety."
  },
  {
    "name_en": "Yi",
    "name_zh": "伊",
    "race_en": "Human",
    "race_zh": "人類",
