    "record_zh": "伊是M伯爵手下的情報員。他在阿爾芬諾之禮篇出現，參與廢墟之母、M伯爵、計畫討論與救援行動。她曾與伊努、帕拉丁、蘇加魯、圖伊特、華生等人一同行動，面對麥丁頓災後的異變與母親相關事件。\n\n之後伊短暫出現在潛伏的危機與深入洛森相關章節，包括劇院之下與月光狩獵會。覆羽莊園篇中，她也在過往命運相關事件裡再度出現。\n\n後續，伊在巫妖之手篇中再度登場，透露自己計畫潛入安德烈亞的研究室拯救蘿琳；龍恩在衝突中將他敲暈，波則扛著昏迷的伊前往目的地。",
    "record_en": "Yi was an intelligence agent under Count M. She appeared in the Gift of Alfenor arc and took part in events involving the Mother of Ruins, Count M, planning discussions, and rescue operations. She acted alongside Inu, Paladin, Sugalu, Tweeter, Watson, and others while facing the abnormalities after the Mattington disaster and incidents related to Mother.\n\nYi later appeared briefly in chapters connected to the Hidden Crisis and Into Losen, including Under the Theater and the Moonlight Hunt. In the Feathered Estate arc, she also appeared again in events tied to past fate.\n\nLater, Yi appeared again in the Hand of the Lich, revealing that she planned to infiltrate Andrea's laboratory to rescue Roline. During the conflict, Ron knocked her unconscious, and Bo carried the unconscious Yi toward the destination."
  },
  {
    "name_en": "Inu",
    "name_zh": "伊努",
    "race_en": "Spirit",
    "race_zh": "精靈",
