    "record_zh": "伊努為 YHWH 柴犬玩偶型態施法工具中寄宿的靈魂，幻化成一名小男童作為其真身。他在麥丁頓破碎篇加入隊伍，從交易與真實形態開始，與帕拉丁、蘇加魯、圖伊特、華生一同面對災後局勢。阿爾芬諾之禮中，他身上出現蜘蛛王相關詛咒，被半神丹尼斯檢查後得知若不前往深淵處理，一到兩週內可能死亡。\n\n在麥克嵩王宮事件中，伊努與圖伊特、帕拉丁、奧利佛一同逃離伊什頓大人的辦公室。奧利佛被衛兵殺死後，伊努以傳送方式把奧利佛的屍體移到自己手上，避免屍體被帶走。之後他參與劇院之下、母親重生與複製體相關事件，也跟著隊伍面對阿爾芬諾、母親與救援計畫的後續，最終以其獨有的傳送能力消失了。",
    "record_en": "Inu was a soul dwelling inside YHWH's Shiba Inu doll-shaped spellcasting focus, manifesting in his true form as a small boy. He joined the party in the Shattered Mattington arc, starting from the Deal and True Form, and faced the post-disaster situation together with Paladin, Sugalu, Tweeter, and Watson. In the Gift of Alfenor, a curse connected to the Spider King appeared on him, and after the demigod Dennis examined him, he learned that he might die within one to two weeks if he did not go to the Abyss to deal with it.\n\nDuring the Macksohn palace incident, Inu fled Lord Ishton's office with Tweeter, Paladin, and Oliver. After Oliver was killed by guards, Inu teleported Oliver's corpse into his own hands to prevent the body from being taken away. He later took part in events connected to Under the Theater, Mother's Rebirth, and the clones, and followed the party through the aftermath of Alfenor, Mother, and the rescue plan. In the end, he disappeared through his distinctive teleportation ability."
  },
  {
    "name_en": "Lott",
    "name_zh": "羅特",
    "race_en": "Tiefling",
    "race_zh": "魔人",
