    ],
    "record_zh": "羅特原為伊照顧的孤兒小弟，在阿爾芬諾之禮後段加入冒險團隊，參與救援行動，之後走過潛伏的危機、深入洛森。他面對所有團隊成員之死，唯有他存活的悲劇，甚至遺忘他所鍾愛的圖伊特相關的記憶，被迫成長。數年後，羅特與新的冒險團隊經歷在一次的神秘委託下去尋找月神的王冠，經歷卓茲蘭之穴，在覆羽莊園見證自己的委託者躍升成神。後續也參與月蝕之席與派琶的預示。他在洛森王國學習妖精語與長笛，也經歷複製體、月光狩獵會與洛森深處的事件。\n\n覆羽莊園後，羅特與烏波、賽柏沿著烏波的直覺前往斐納札；GoR 在抵達前一夜失蹤。斐納札中，羅特以單音節化名「蘭」行動，接觸譚，調查衣服顏色、議會與工作制度。他對芬諾爾信仰產生排斥，並透過覆羽莊園取得的面具與愛神阿莫雷特締約。派琶預示篇中，他追尋賽柏下落，並照顧從死亡邊緣回歸的佛拉。",
    "record_en": "Lott was originally an orphan younger brother cared for by Yi, and joined the adventuring party in the later part of the Gift of Alfenor to take part in the rescue operation. He later went through the Hidden Crisis and Into Losen. He faced the tragedy in which every member of the party died and only he survived, and he even forgot the memories related to Tweeter, whom he loved, forcing him to grow up. Years later, Lott and a new adventuring party accepted another mysterious commission to search for the moon god's crown, went through the Cave of Drogsland, and witnessed his client ascend to godhood at the Feathered Estate. He later also took part in the Seat of the Lunar Eclipse and Py'Par's Prophecy. In the Kingdom of Losen, he learned Sylvan and the flute, and experienced the clones, the Moonlight Hunt, and events deep within Losen.\n\nAfter the Feathered Estate, Lott, Ubbo, and Psyber followed Ubbo's intuition toward Fenazza; GoR disappeared the night before they arrived. In Fenazza, Lott operated under the single-syllable alias \"Lan,\" contacted Tan, and investigated clothing colors, the council, and the work system. He developed aversion toward the faith of Fenor, and made a pact with the god of love Amoret through the mask obtained at the Feathered Estate. In Py'Par's Prophecy, he pursued Psyber's whereabouts and cared for Phola after she returned from the edge of death."
  },
  {
    "name_en": "Al-lon",
    "name_zh": "阿龍",
    "race_en": "Dragonborn",
    "race_zh": "龍人",
    "class_en": [
      "Barbarian"
    ],
    "class_zh": [
      "野蠻人"
    ],
    "player": "仰山",
    "guest": "0",
    "campaign": [
      "Rugatha WILDS"
    ],
    "record_zh": "阿龍在貿易之都貝瑟頓開始冒險，與毛毛、鑰、雷亞、羅羅一同接觸幽深林與 T.I.D.E.S. 相關線索。他在酒館詢問菸草，拿出父親留下的小煙斗試抽，也在幽深林與海妖墓場中面對骷髏與歌聲。\n\n在第1410頁書店，鑰讀到《喬里森與其神話》中「從河流漂下的孩子是喬里森選中之子」的內容，與阿龍以蛋的形態順流而來的身世相符。之後阿龍參與 T.I.D.E.S. 的邀請、天選者集會。\n\n在土城風暴中，阿龍回到從小長大的家鄉「土城」，與父母相見、與青梅竹馬佩妮重逢，卻得知佩妮心有所屬、參與剿山賊，最終卻被逐出土城，剝奪其姓氏。\n\n拉撒拿繼承人事件中，阿龍見到自己的原生家庭，但也在與銀龍對話的隔天，目睹父母之死。在冒險團的偵破下，以本名賽拉尼爾・艾瑞利斯繼任拉撒拿龍冠的阿龍，親自宣判堂妹奈梨莎的罪行。\n\n阿龍在與冒險者們來到克萊芬時，接獲情敵大奧斯的消息，而趕回拉撒拿，暫時離開了冒險團。",
    "record_en": "Al-lon began his adventure in the trade city of Betheton, encountering clues related to the Deepwood and T.I.D.E.S. together with Fur, Kaname, Leah, and Roel. At a tavern, he asked about tobacco and tried smoking the small pipe left by his father. In the Deepwood and the Siren Graveyard, he faced skeletons and song.\n\nAt Page 1410 Books, Kaname read a passage in Jorisan and His Myths saying that a child drifting down the river was the chosen child of Jorisan, which matched Al-lon's origin of arriving downstream in egg form. Al-lon then took part in the T.I.D.E.S. invitation and the Chosen gathering.\n\nDuring the Storm of Tucheng, Al-lon returned to Tucheng, the hometown where he had grown up, met his parents, and reunited with his childhood friend Penny. He learned that Penny's heart belonged to someone else, joined the campaign against the bandits, and was ultimately expelled from Tucheng and stripped of his surname.\n\nIn the Rasanna Heir incident, Al-lon met his birth family, but the day after speaking with the silver dragon, he witnessed his parents' deaths. After the adventuring party's investigation, Al-lon, under his true name Selaniel Aerylis, inherited the dragon crown of Rasanna and personally pronounced judgment on his cousin Narissa.\n\nWhen Al-lon reached Kleifen with the adventurers, he received news about his romantic rival, Big Os, and returned to Rasanna, temporarily leaving the party."
  },
  {
    "name_en": "Roel",
    "name_zh": "羅羅",
    "race_en": "Elf",
    "race_zh": "妖精",
    "class_en": [
      "Warlock"
    ],
    "class_zh": [
      "契術師"
