    ],
    "record_zh": "羅羅在冒險初期以身分不明的妖精加入隊伍，同行者一度懷疑他可能是通緝犯。他表示自己的許多行動與神秘的「祂」有關。貝瑟頓期間，他與雷亞前往糖果店與破舊甜點店，購買大量甜食。\n\n在幽深林與海妖墓場事件中，羅羅以遠距離攻擊協助同伴擊倒骷髏。之後他參與 T.I.D.E.S. 的邀請、天選者集會、土城風暴、拉撒拿繼承人與不被承認的孩子等事件。土城後期，他與毛毛在掛衣間偷聽老樹盟與市民連線相關交談，也在拉比帶領下於夜間外出調查利斯達上校相關線索。",
    "record_en": "Roel joined the party early in the adventure as a fey of unknown identity, and his companions once suspected that he might be a wanted criminal. He said that many of his actions were connected to the mysterious \"Him.\" During the Betheton period, he went with Leah to a candy shop and an old dessert shop, buying large amounts of sweets.\n\nDuring the Deepwood and Siren Graveyard incidents, Roel helped his companions defeat skeletons with ranged attacks. He later took part in the T.I.D.E.S. invitation, the Chosen gathering, the Storm of Tucheng, the Rasanna Heir, and the Unacknowledged Child. Late in Tucheng, he and Fur eavesdropped in a coatroom on conversations related to the Old Tree League and the Citizens' Line, and under Ravi's guidance, went out at night to investigate clues related to Colonel Lisda."
  },
  {
    "name_en": "Dawn Light Fur",
    "name_zh": "毛毛",
    "race_en": "Tabaxi",
    "race_zh": "班貓人",
    "class_en": [
