    "record_zh": "毛毛在貿易之都開始與冒險團同行。他從小在貝瑟頓生活，熟悉貝瑟頓店家與街道，也在幽深林中爬上樹偵查，發現巡守衛兵。海妖墓場戰鬥中，他受重傷後逃進小木屋休息，之後與同伴擊倒骷髏。夜晚守夜時，阿龍曾試圖剪他腳上的毛做耳塞，毛毛因此醒來並感到不滿。\n\n毛毛與第1410頁書店熟識，店員湯普生以他的全名黎輝毛稱呼他，也為他準備雞腿。後續他參與 T.I.D.E.S.、土城風暴與拉撒拿繼承人事件。土城後期，他跟蹤可疑黑衣人，發現對方談到辯論會場地與槍擊；皮尼歐教授遇刺後，他也試圖用尾巴悄悄取走瑪莉貝爾手中的槍械。",
    "record_en": "Fur began traveling with the adventuring party in the trade city. He had lived in Betheton since childhood, knew the city's shops and streets, and climbed trees to scout in the Deepwood, discovering patrolling guards. In the Siren Graveyard battle, he was badly wounded and fled into a small cabin to rest, then later helped his companions defeat the skeletons. During the night watch, Al-lon tried to cut fur from his foot to make earplugs, causing Fur to wake and become displeased.\n\nFur was familiar with Page 1410 Books. The clerk Thompson addressed him by his full name, Dawn Light Fur, and prepared a chicken leg for him. He later took part in T.I.D.E.S., the Storm of Tucheng, and the Rasanna Heir. Late in Tucheng, he followed suspicious people in black and discovered that they were discussing the debate venue and a shooting. After Professor Pinio was assassinated, he also tried to quietly take the gun from Maribel's hand with his tail."
  },
