    "record_zh": "鑰在乘著推車同行，從貝瑟頓到幽深林一路照顧同伴。她安置被雷亞抓到的松鼠頹哥，並將牠命名為嘎吱爵士，使牠在推車中安定下來。海妖墓場戰鬥中，她以輔助協助隊伍擊倒骷髏。\n\n之後鑰參與 T.I.D.E.S. 的邀請、天選者集會、土城風暴、拉撒拿繼承人與不被承認的孩子等事件。土城後期，她以傳訊術聯絡被送往診所的拉比，讓拉比得知皮尼歐教授遇刺、城市陷入動亂。",
    "record_en": "Kaname traveled along with a cart, caring for her companions from Betheton to the Deepwood. She settled the squirrel that Leah had caught, Tuigo, named it Sir Squeak, and helped it calm down in the cart. In the Siren Graveyard battle, she supported the party in defeating the skeletons.\n\nKaname later took part in the T.I.D.E.S. invitation, the Chosen gathering, the Storm of Tucheng, the Rasanna Heir, and the Unacknowledged Child. Late in Tucheng, she used Sending to contact Ravi, who had been taken to a clinic, letting him know that Professor Pinio had been assassinated and that the city had fallen into unrest."
  },
  {
