    ],
    "record_zh": "巴斯在月蝕之席篇加入冒險團，與羅特、烏波等人面對斐納札後續與賽柏失蹤的狀況。派琶的預示篇中，他扛著虛弱的羅特，跟著烏波追尋賽柏留下的痕跡，進入一座不斷提醒外人「別在夜晚離開這裡」的村莊。\n\n在村莊裡，巴斯與村民、孩子互動，教一名年輕人玩牌，也與烏波討論村莊的古怪處。離開村莊後，他繼續與羅特、烏波前往派琶所在之處，參與面具下的真相、巨蛇之勢與常翠林相關事件。旅途中，他也在佛拉事件中對羅特治療敵人一事感到不滿，並當場質問羅特。",
    "record_en": "Buzz joined the adventuring party in the Seat of the Lunar Eclipse arc, facing the aftermath of Fenazza and Psyber's disappearance together with Lott, Ubbo, and others. In Py'Par's Prophecy, he carried the weakened Lott, followed Ubbo in tracing the signs left by Psyber, and entered a village that repeatedly warned outsiders not to leave at night.\n\nIn the village, Buzz interacted with the villagers and children, taught a young person to play cards, and discussed the village's oddities with Ubbo. After leaving the village, he continued with Lott and Ubbo toward Py'Par's location, taking part in the Truth Beneath the Mask, the Serpent's Momentum, and events related to the Evergreen Forest. During the journey, he was also dissatisfied when Lott treated the enemy in the Phola incident, and questioned Lott on the spot."
