    "record_zh": "冒險團在前往洛森時遇見帕斯卡，得知他是帕拉丁的兄弟；他聽聞帕拉丁在麥克嵩死亡的消息後，前往洛森尋找可能知道帕拉丁消息的人，並在途中與冒險者相遇。\n\n帕斯卡之後與羅特、蘇加魯、圖伊特等人一同行動，經歷月光狩獵會、孵化而出的夥伴等事件。他加入時，隊伍正在洛森王國內尋找蜘蛛神教與母親相關線索，也要面對非妖精在洛森過夜可能遭遇危險的問題。",
    "record_en": "The adventuring party met Pascal on the way to Losen and learned that he was Paladin's brother. After hearing that Paladin had died in Macksohn, he went to Losen to search for people who might know news about Paladin, and met the adventurers on the way.\n\nPascal then acted together with Lott, Sugalu, Tweeter, and others, going through events such as the Moonlight Hunt and the Hatched Companion. When he joined, the party was searching within the Kingdom of Losen for clues related to the Spider God cult and Mother, while also facing the danger that non-fey might encounter if they spent the night in Losen."
  },
