    "record_zh": "雷亞加入冒險團隊，與阿龍、毛毛、鑰、羅羅一起從貝瑟頓前往幽深林。海妖墓場戰鬥中，雷亞施放雲霧術限制視線，並以近戰攻擊參與擊倒骷髏。\n\n之後雷亞參與 T.I.D.E.S.、天選者集會、土城風暴與拉撒拿繼承人事件。\n\n在拉撒拿，雷亞從銀龍口中得知自己家鄉的事，而來到她龍人血脈的家鄉，克萊芬。隨後雷亞與冒險團隊被迫以間諜身份潛入她蜥蜴人血脈的家鄉，萊斯諾，意外捲入政治鬥爭。雷亞所支持的新書院皮尼歐教授遇刺時，她跳上舞台試圖以醫藥技巧搶救教授，但教授胸口被炸開，衛兵也將她推開。秘書長瓦羅恩接掌新書院後，雷亞試圖與她激辯，卻被對方一指點到雙腿發麻而跪下。老樹盟派了立德上尉接觸雷亞，想利用其混血的身份為老樹盟站台。",
    "record_en": "Leah joined the adventuring party and traveled from Betheton to the Deepwood with Al-lon, Fur, Kaname, and Roel. In the Siren Graveyard battle, Leah cast Fog Cloud to limit visibility and joined the fight against the skeletons in melee.\n\nLeah later took part in T.I.D.E.S., the Chosen gathering, the Storm of Tucheng, and the Rasanna Heir.\n\nIn Rasanna, Leah learned from the silver dragon about her homeland, then came to Kleifen, the homeland of her dragonborn bloodline. Afterward, Leah and the adventuring party were forced to infiltrate Lesno, the homeland of her lizardfolk bloodline, as spies, unexpectedly becoming involved in a political struggle. When Professor Pinio of the New Academy, whom Leah supported, was assassinated, she jumped onto the stage and tried to save him with medical skill, but the professor's chest had been blown open and guards pushed her away. After Secretary-General Valorn took control of the New Academy, Leah tried to argue with her, but Valorn touched her with one finger and numbed her legs, causing her to kneel. The Old Tree League sent Lieutenant Lide to contact Leah, hoping to use her mixed-blood identity to speak for the Old Tree League."
  },
