    "record_zh": "華生在麥丁頓破碎篇登場，與帕拉丁、蘇加魯、圖伊特、墜兒等在惡棍之城瑟巴諾成為夥伴。她參與交易、真實形態與阿爾芬諾之禮。阿爾芬諾事件中，她以化名露西亞小姐接觸貴族，也在舊城區見到母親大人，得知貧民窟居民受到她幫助。\n\n在潘蜜拉家與伯納德相關事件中，華生與同伴發現母親大人的臥房裡有巨型繭，並在門口發現伯納德乾枯的屍體。暴民放火後，華生抱起伯納德，與扛著圖伊特的蘇加魯、帕拉丁趁機逃走。後續她在來到洛森王國後，因戴上月光狩獵會的面具，而消失不見，只留下她的懷錶。",
    "record_en": "Watson appeared in the Shattered Mattington arc and became companions with Paladin, Sugalu, Tweeter, Drayer, and others in Sebano, the City of Villains. She took part in the Deal, True Form, and Gift of Alfenor. During the Alfenor incident, she used the alias Miss Lucia to contact nobles, and also met Mother in the old district, learning that she had helped the residents of the slums.\n\nDuring the events at Pamela's house and those related to Bernard, Watson and her companions found a giant cocoon in Mother's bedroom, and discovered Bernard's dried corpse at the doorway. After the mob set the fire, Watson picked up Bernard and escaped with Sugalu, who was carrying Tweeter, and Paladin. Later, after reaching the Kingdom of Losen, she disappeared after putting on a Moonlight Hunt mask, leaving only her pocket watch behind."
  },
