    "record_zh": "蘇加魯先在麥丁頓餘波中登場。家亨與安納戴克死後，他與帕拉丁爵士、墜兒分家前往瑟巴諾追查拉索斯教。之後他與帕拉丁、圖伊特、華生等人走入惡棍之城，參與交易、真實形態與阿爾芬諾之禮。\n\n阿爾芬諾相關事件中，蘇加魯曾被神王呼喚回去。深入洛森時，他以外貌略有變化的新身份「艾倫・卓茲克」短暫回到隊伍；他的膚色與衣著都與過去不同，對神王的態度也轉為崇敬。月光狩獵會襲擊後，眾人清醒時發現剛回歸的艾倫又不見了，買給佛拉的酒也被他帶走，間接成為佛拉戒酒的一大契機。",
    "record_en": "Sugalu first appeared in the aftermath of Mattington. After Jiaheng and Anedak died, he split off with Syr Paladin and Drayer to go to Sebano and investigate the Rathos cult. He later entered the City of Villains with Paladin, Tweeter, Watson, and others, taking part in the Deal, True Form, and Gift of Alfenor.\n\nDuring the Alfenor-related events, Sugalu was once called back by the God-King. In Into Losen, he briefly returned to the party under a new identity, Allen Drogske, with a slightly changed appearance; his skin color and clothing differed from before, and his attitude toward the God-King had turned reverent. After the Moonlight Hunt attack, when everyone woke up, they found that the recently returned Allen had disappeared again. The alcohol he had bought for Phola had also been taken with him, indirectly becoming a major trigger for Phola to stop drinking."
