    "record_zh": "安納戴克在麥克嵩篇後段加入主線，參與上流生活、闇影之父、角鬥士與麥丁頓餘波等事件。他在地下行動中與隊伍調查拉茲特獸、闇影之父與瑟巴諾相關線索，也曾在火勢與爆炸後身受重傷，由帕拉丁以治療法術救回。\n\n比武大會慘劇後，安納戴克與家亨、雷米離去後沒有回來。雷米後來宣稱三人遭到惡徒圍毆，只有自己逃出。隊伍沿城牆西北方找到安納戴克與家亨的遺體：安納戴克的身體被斬首，左手將家亨的頭按置在地上。眾人挖墓後將他與家亨安葬。",
    "record_en": "Anedak joined the main story in the later part of the Macksohn arc, taking part in Upper Life, Father of Shadows, the Gladiator, and the aftermath of Mattington. During underground operations, he and the party investigated clues related to the Razte beast, the Father of Shadows, and Sebano. He was also badly wounded after fire and explosions, and Paladin saved him with healing magic.\n\nAfter the tragedy at the tournament, Anedak left with Jiaheng and Lemmy and did not return. Lemmy later claimed that the three had been surrounded and beaten by villains, and that only he escaped. The party found Anedak's and Jiaheng's bodies northwest along the city wall: Anedak's body had been decapitated, and his left hand had placed Jiaheng's head on the ground. The group dug a grave and buried him together with Jiaheng."
