    "record_zh": "烏波在卓茲蘭之穴篇加入冒險團隊，與 GoR、庫登、羅特、賽柏等人接觸孽物、芬諾爾傳道者與羽王。覆羽莊園後，他依循直覺，與羅特、賽柏花了一個月前往自己的出生地；抵達前，GoR 在守夜時沒有留下訊息便消失。\n\n在斐納札，烏波被唐歡迎回家，卻察覺關於出生地的記憶像是被植入腦中。他以單音節化名「波」行動，會自然跟隨鐘聲跪下，也熟悉月神禱詞。夢中，他得到芬諾爾神諭與新的能力。",
    "record_en": "Ubbo joined the adventuring party in the Cave of Drogsland arc, encountering the wretched creatures, Fenor missionaries, and the Feather King together with GoR, Kudan, Lott, Psyber, and others. After the Feathered Estate, he followed his intuition, traveling for a month with Lott and Psyber toward his birthplace; before they arrived, GoR disappeared during the night watch without leaving any message.\n\nIn Fenazza, Ubbo was welcomed home by Tang, but noticed that his memories of his birthplace seemed to have been implanted in his mind. He operated under the single-syllable alias \"Bo,\" would naturally kneel when the bells rang, and was familiar with prayers to the moon god. In a dream, he received an oracle from Fenor and gained a new ability."
