    "record_zh": "賽柏在卓茲蘭之穴篇加入冒險團隊，與 GoR、庫登、羅特、烏波等人面對孽物入門、芬諾爾傳道者與羽王。覆羽莊園後，他與羅特陪同烏波追尋出生地的直覺。\n\n在斐納札，賽柏以單音節化名「潤」行動，和羅特、烏波一起被要求穿上外來者衣服，進入溫室工作並搬土。用餐時，他勉強吃下乾草，但吃不下土，將自己的份給了烏波。鐘聲響起時，賽柏會自動跪下。月蝕之席後段，賽柏一度失蹤，羅特、烏波與巴斯在派琶的預示篇追尋他的下落。",
    "record_en": "Psyber joined the adventuring party in the Cave of Drogsland arc, facing the wretched creatures, Fenor missionaries, and the Feather King together with GoR, Kudan, Lott, Ubbo, and others. After the Feathered Estate, he accompanied Lott in following Ubbo's intuition toward his birthplace.\n\nIn Fenazza, Psyber operated under the single-syllable alias \"Run.\" Along with Lott and Ubbo, he was required to wear outsiders' clothing, enter the greenhouse to work, and move soil. During a meal, he forced himself to eat hay, but could not eat soil, and gave his portion to Ubbo. When the bells rang, Psyber would automatically kneel. In the later part of the Seat of the Lunar Eclipse, Psyber disappeared for a time, and Lott, Ubbo, and Buzz searched for his whereabouts in Py'Par's Prophecy."
