    "record_en": "Drayer first appeared with Sugalu in the aftermath of Mattington. After Jiaheng and Anedak died, she split off with Syr Paladin and Sugalu to go to Sebano and investigate the Rathos cult, nominally to avenge their dead companions. Later, in Rugatha lite's City of Villains arc, she traveled with Paladin, Sugalu, Tweeter, and Watson.\n\nIn the later part of the City of Villains arc, Drayer revealed before the adventurers and Hob that she was a spy of the Rathos cult. She vanished through a teleportation circle and did not continue traveling with the party."
