    "record_zh": "布朗的冒險從接受溫德家的護衛委託開始。他計畫護送溫德一家穿越森林，但聽見「殺了溫德」的低語，也遇上失蹤又回來的巴哥犬瑪芬先生。\n\n獨自抵達魏斯科後，他在酒館被梅莉與瑪蒂達下藥，醒來時被扔進服從神社地下室，四周坐滿乾枯屍骨。\n\n為了找回瑪芬先生，布朗追查梅莉、瑪蒂達與黑蓮花，並在服從神社地下室經歷受洗。他在無限黑暗中失去部分記憶，又被卡魯神父告知自己將走上拉索斯之路。離開魏斯科後，他用黑蓮花花瓣換得馬匹，前往夏庭森途中認識魔術師羅納德，並確認瑪芬先生能變成野狼。",
    "record_en": "Brown's adventure began with accepting an escort commission from the Wind family. He planned to escort the Winds through the forest, but heard whispers saying, \"Kill Wind,\" and also encountered Mr. Muffin, a pug who had disappeared and returned.\n\nAfter reaching Weisco alone, he was drugged by Melly and Matilda at the tavern. When he woke, he had been thrown into the basement of the Shrine of Obedience, surrounded by dried corpses.\n\nTo find Mr. Muffin, Brown investigated Melly, Matilda, and the Black Lotus, and underwent baptism in the basement of the Shrine of Obedience. In endless darkness, he lost part of his memory, and Father Karu told him that he would walk the path of Rathos. After leaving Weisco, he traded Black Lotus petals for a horse, met the magician Ronald on the way to Shatinson, and confirmed that Mr. Muffin could transform into a dire wolf."
