    "record_zh": "賽希爾在 WILDS 的天選者集會篇客串登場。他以 T.I.D.E.S. 成員身份，參與奢華盛宴與集結事件，與阿龍、毛毛、鑰、雷亞、羅羅等人一同身處 T.I.D.E.S. 相關集會與宴會場合。當時隊伍已從里奇蒙爵士接觸到 T.I.D.E.S. 的組織結構。\n\n在集會中，眾人得知 T.I.D.E.S. 的編制與高層變動，也見到萊里被宣布不再是方尖碑成員與 T.I.D.E.S. 成員。被萊里邀請的冒險者也被要求離場。",
    "record_en": "Cecil made a guest appearance in WILDS during the Chosen Gathering arc. As a member of T.I.D.E.S., she took part in the Luxury Feast and Gathering events, attending T.I.D.E.S.-related meetings and banquet occasions together with Al-lon, Fur, Kaname, Leah, Roel, and others. At that time, the party had already learned about T.I.D.E.S.'s organizational structure through Syr Richmond.\n\nDuring the gathering, the group learned about T.I.D.E.S.'s organization and changes among its leadership, and also saw Larry announced as no longer being a member of the Obelisk or T.I.D.E.S. The adventurers invited by Larry were also asked to leave."
