    "record_zh": "拉比在 WILDS 的不被承認的孩子篇登場，陪同隊伍進入陌生的家鄉、藍色紅色與土色，以及雷亞的困境等事件。他加入時，土城與新曙光相關衝突升高，老樹盟、市民連線、新書院與軍方之間的關係逐漸惡化。\n\n皮尼歐教授遇刺前夕，拉比因槍傷被送往診所。他透過鑰的傳訊得知教授死亡與城市動亂，撐著虛弱身體離開診所，朝酒館返回。傳訊術耗盡後，他呼叫自己的梟，捎口信給斷訊的鑰。回到酒館後，他與冒險者會合，主張調查城市局勢，並提出先到隔壁包廂討論的折衷方案。",
    "record_en": "Ravi appeared in WILDS during the Unacknowledged Child arc, accompanying the party into the events of the unfamiliar hometown, blue, red, and earth colors, and Leah's predicament. When he joined, the conflicts related to Tucheng and New Dawn were escalating, and relations among the Old Tree League, Citizens' Line, New Academy, and the military were gradually worsening.\n\nOn the eve of Professor Pinio's assassination, Ravi was sent to a clinic because of a gunshot wound. Through Kaname's Sending, he learned of the professor's death and the city's unrest, then left the clinic despite his weakened body and headed back toward the tavern. After Sending was exhausted, he called his owl and sent a verbal message to Kaname, whose communication had been cut off. After returning to the tavern, he regrouped with the adventurers, argued for investigating the city situation, and proposed the compromise of first discussing matters in the private room next door."
